se.lexicon.garage

Class Garage

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.lexicon.garage.Garage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GarageInterface<Vehicle>

    public class Garage
extends java.lang.Object
implements GarageInterface<Vehicle>
    This class represents a garage. The users can park different types of vehicles. E.g. cars and boats. The garage utilizes MySQL for data storage.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Systemtestarna 2019
